<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Deliberate2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Deliberate,</orth> adj., considerate: <cit><quote>these d. fools,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 2.9.80" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 9, 80</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>your most grave belly was d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 1.1.131" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 1, 131</bibl></cit>. Of things: <cit><quote>whose settled visage and d. word,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 3.1.90" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. III, 1, 90</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>d. pause,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 4.3.9" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 3, 9</bibl></cit>.
